                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 relative">
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <!-- Screenshot 1 -->
                    <div
                        class="glass-card p-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 relative"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="bg-navy-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden aspect-video flex items-center justify-center border border-white/5"
                        >
                            <img
                                src="/revision.png"
                                alt="Interface de lecture des fiches"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                                loading="lazy"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Screenshot 2 -->
                    <div
                        class="glass-card p-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 relative"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="bg-navy-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden aspect-video flex items-center justify-center border border-white/5"
                        >
                            <img
                                src="/revision-2.png"
                                alt="Référentiels et podcasts"
                                class="w-full h-full object-cover"
                                loading="lazy"
                            />
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section Journal Hebdo -->
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-16 mb-32">
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 text-xs font-medium mb-6"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-4 h-4 mr-2"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        ><path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M19 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v1m2 13a2 2 0 01-2-2V7m2 13a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2m-4-3H9M7 16h6M7 8h6v4H7V8z"
                        ></path></svg
                    >
                    Journal Hebdo
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                    Restez connecté à l'actualité <span class="text-amber-400">sapeur-pompier</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                    Chaque semaine, recevez l'essentiel de l'actualité pompier et de la veille réglementaire en un seul endroit.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-amber-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-1 mr-4"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold">
                                Actualités SDIS
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                                Les dernières nouvelles des services d'incendie et de secours.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-amber-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-1 mr-4"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold">
                                Veille réglementaire
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                                Décrets, arrêtés et textes officiels à ne pas manquer.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-amber-500/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-1 mr-4"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
                            >
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-white font-semibold">
                                RETEX terrain
                            </h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
                                Retours d'expérience et analyses d'interventions.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <!-- Widget PWA Mockup -->
            <div class="lg:w-1/2 relative">
                <div class="max-w-sm mx-auto">
                    <div
                        class="glass-card p-2 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 relative"
                    >
                        <div class="bg-navy-800 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 overflow-hidden">
                            <!-- Header -->
                            <div class="px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                    <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-red-500/15 border border-red-500/30 flex items-center justify-center">
                                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 20H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h10a2 2 0 012 2v1m2 13a2 2 0 01-2-2V7m2 13a2 2 0 002-2V9a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2m-4-3H9M7 16h6M7 8h6v4H7V8z"></path>
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <h3 class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">Journal Pompier</h3>
                                        <p class="text-gray-500 text-xs">Votre veille métier</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <!-- Bulletin Item -->
                            <div class="px-4 pb-3">
                                <div class="bg-navy-900/50 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 flex items-center justify-between">
                                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-gray-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                                        </svg>
                                        <span class="text-gray-300 text-sm">Bulletin de la semaine</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <span class="px-2 py-0.5 bg-teal-500/20 text-teal-400 text-[10px] font-bold rounded uppercase tracking-wide">
                                        Nouveau
                                    </span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <!-- Footer -->
                            <div class="px-4 pb-4">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-gray-500">
                                    <span class="w-4 h-4 bg-red-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-[10px] font-bold">1</span>
                                    <span>bulletin non lu</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 2: S'entraîner -->
        <div
            class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-16 mb-32"
        >
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                <div
                    class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-accent/30 bg-accent/10 text-accent text-xs font-medium mb-6"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-4 h-4 mr-2"
                        fill="none"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        ><path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg
                    >
                    S'entraîner
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">
                    Préparez-vous aux conditions réelles
                </h2>
                <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                    Testez vos compétences théoriques grâce aux fonctionnalités dédiées à la préparation aux examens de sélection ou concours.
                </p>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start">
                        <div
                            class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center mt-1 mr-4"
                        >
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4 text-accent"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                ><path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg
